#: done.py:137
msgid ""
"ISO-8601 formatted string representing the start date of this assignment. We"
" ignore this."
msgstr ""
"ISO-8601 formateret streng, der angiver startdatoen for denne opgave. Vi "
"ignorerer denne."

#: done.py:142
msgid ""
